<p>In order to help you to organize your project, we have broken the requirements into four separate iterations. It is expected that you will complete iterations 1-3, while 4 includes extensions that represent opportunities to further explore.</p>

<ul>
  <li><a href="./iteration_1">Iteration 1</a></li>
  <li><a href="./iteration_2">Iteration 2</a></li>
  <li><a href="./iteration_3">Iteration 3</a></li>
  <li><a href="./iteration_4">Iteration 4</a></li>
</ul>

<p>In addition to the functionality outlined in these iterations, we will expect the you to do the following:</p>

<ul>
  <li>write tests for each class</li>
  <li>write readable code</li>
  <li>make frequent commits</li>
  <li>use pull requests</li>
</ul>

<p>For more detailed information about what we expect, please review the <a href="./rubric">rubric</a> before starting this project!</p>
